This function provides a print method for the class "plsRmodel"

Arguments

x

an object of the class "plsRmodel"
...

not used

Value

NULL

Examples


data(Cornell)
XCornell<-Cornell[,1:7]
yCornell<-Cornell[,8]
modpls <- plsRglm(yCornell,XCornell,3,modele="pls")
